<Defs>
  <IncidentDef>
    <defName>Kurin_FoxInBlackJoin</defName>
    <label>黑衣魅狐</label>
    <category>Special</category>
    <targetTags>
      <li>Map_PlayerHome</li>
    </targetTags>
    <workerClass>IncidentWorker_WandererJoin</workerClass>
    <letterLabel>Fox In Black</letterLabel>
    <letterText>察觉到麻烦，神秘的[PAWN_kind]来了。\n\n[PAWN_pronoun]能解决麻烦吗？</letterText>
    <baseChance>0</baseChance>
    <minRefireDays>10</minRefireDays>
    <minGreatestPopulation>1</minGreatestPopulation>
    <pawnKind>Kurin_Fox_In_Black</pawnKind>
    <pawnMustBeCapableOfViolence>true</pawnMustBeCapableOfViolence>
  </IncidentDef>
  <IncidentDef>
    <defName>Kurin_WandererJoin</defName>
    <label>流浪的魅狐加入</label>
    <category>Misc</category>
    <targetTags>
      <li>Map_PlayerHome</li>
    </targetTags>
    <workerClass>IncidentWorker_WandererJoin</workerClass>
    <letterLabel>Wanderer kurin joins: {PAWN_nameDef}</letterLabel>
    <letterText>一个名为{PAWN_nameDef}的{PAWN_title}挥舞着三条美丽的尾巴来到这里并加入。\n\n拥有三条狐尾巴的魅狐，除了他们自己的种族之外，对其他人都漠不关心。如果殖民地里的魅狐数量相对较少，那么魅狐会感到孤独，反之亦然，如果魅狐的数量相对较多，魅狐会感到高兴。如果你与其他魅狐殖民地为敌，他们会惊讶你居然是个叛徒。如果你不欢迎{PAWN_nameDef}，可以放逐{PAWN_objective}，将{PAWN_objective}卖给奴隶贩子，或者简单地杀掉。但其他人可能会因此而感到不安。</letterText>
    <baseChance>0.8</baseChance>
    <minRefireDays>45</minRefireDays>
    <earliestDay>15</earliestDay>
    <pawnKind>Kurin_Colonist</pawnKind>
    <populationEffect>IncreaseMedium</populationEffect>
  </IncidentDef>
  <IncidentDef>
    <defName>Kimiri_WandererJoin</defName>
    <label>缓刑犯奇龙加入</label>
    <category>Misc</category>
    <targetTags>
      <li>Map_PlayerHome</li>
    </targetTags>
    <workerClass>IncidentWorker_WandererJoin</workerClass>
    <letterLabel>Probationer kimiri joins: {PAWN_nameDef}</letterLabel>
    <letterText>一个名为{PAWN_nameDef}的{PAWN_title}挥舞着美丽的尾巴来到这里并加入。\n\n{PAWN_nameDef}发现{PAWN_possessive}生活很无聊，所以{PAWN_nameDef}决定离开魅狐移民船，加入你的阵营。如果你不欢迎{PAWN_nameDef}，可以放逐{PAWN_objective}，将{PAWN_objective}卖给奴隶贩子，或者简单地杀掉。但其他人可能会因此而感到不安。</letterText>
    <baseChance>0.8</baseChance>
    <minRefireDays>45</minRefireDays>
    <earliestDay>15</earliestDay>
    <pawnKind>Kimiri_Probationer</pawnKind>
    <populationEffect>IncreaseMedium</populationEffect>
  </IncidentDef>
